textBeforeTable: Join as a new member or continue your membership by joining at the next member level. AMSA offers its members unprecedented value and benefits, including leadership training, information and resources. community service opportunities, and much more. Check-out our AMSA member benefits. Benefits for Our Members AMSA members are medical students, premedical students, interns, residents and practicing physicians. By joining AMSA, you enhance the power of the community, enabling AMSA to have a greater impact within society as the organization works to improve the well-being of physicians-in-training, protect the integrity of the medical profession, and advance the health of patients. Explore AMSA, engage with peers and the community and thus, make a difference in medicine, your community and your own life. Advance the profession of medicine Contribute to the welfare of medical students, premedical students, interns, residents and post-MD/DO trainees Improve and increase the understanding of world health problems Enhance the social, moral and ethical obligations of the profession of medicine Promote active improvement in medical education Advance the health care and healthcare delivery to all people As the only national independent student-run medical organization working for medical students, the American Medical Student Association (AMSA) is the premier source of learning, knowledge and community for physicians-in-training.
